name: Abyssin
Lore: 'Abyssins have an extremely violent culture. They also possess tremendous regenerative abilities. Often become mercenaries once they leave their homeworld, Byss.',
Text: 'Power +2 and Forfeit +1 while Myo at Audience Chamber. If lost or forfeited during a battle, may use 2 Force to ''regenerate'' (place Abyssin in your Used Pile).',
